397
00:40:57,539 --> 00:40:59,449
Jděte.

398
00:40:59,459 --> 00:41:00,519
Já, jít?

399
00:41:00,519 --> 00:41:02,919
Mizněte!

400
00:41:02,919 --> 00:41:05,229
Tvrdě pracujte.

401
00:41:06,709 --> 00:41:08,859
